  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Keyboard tapping test</measure>
    <time_frame>1 day</time_frame>
    <description>Participants will be asked to tap a key of a computer keyboard as fast as possible in five seconds. They will be asked to do three times. We will measure the number of tapping. The primary outcome will be the averaged data of the numbers.This will be done before and after 5-day rTMS intervention.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
